trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **Navigating** event.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona datos para el evento **Navigating**.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about the navigation that was requested, and are passed to handlers of the **Navigating** event, which is implemented by the following:
trans-unit.target: Estos argumentos de evento contienen información sobre el panel de navegación que se solicitó y se pasa a los controladores de la **Navigating** evento, que es implementado por el texto siguiente:

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> encapsulates the following details of the navigation request:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs> Encapsula los detalles siguientes de la solicitud de navegación:

trans-unit.source: **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **Iniciación de navegación**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.

trans-unit.source: **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **Contenido de navegación**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.

trans-unit.source: **Navigation Request**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **Solicitud de navegación**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.

trans-unit.source: **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **Estado de navegación**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.

trans-unit.source: This information allows you to both evaluate the nature of the navigation request, and view and update specified request details before navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Esta información le permite evaluar la naturaleza de la solicitud de navegación y ver y actualizar los detalles de la solicitud especificado antes de que se produce la navegación.

trans-unit.source: Based on the navigation request information provided by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>, or based on application-specific state or code, you can completely prevent navigation by setting the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true` (by default, <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> is `false`).
trans-unit.target: En función de la información de solicitud de navegación proporcionada por <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs>, o en función del estado de específicos de la aplicación o el código, puede evitar completamente navegación estableciendo la <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> propiedad `true` (de forma predeterminada, <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> es `false`).

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to handle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> to detect whether a request to refresh static content was made, and if one was, how to cancel the request.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se muestra cómo controlar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> para detectar si se realizó una solicitud para actualizar el contenido estático y, si es así, cómo cancelar la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene una referencia al objeto de contenido al que se navega.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Object" /> reference to the content object that is being navigated to; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Referencia de <see cref="T:System.Object" /> al objeto de contenido al que se navega; de lo contrario, es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Puede navegar al contenido mediante una [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] o un objeto.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an object, which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> contains a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Al navegar a un objeto, que se produce cuando se llama a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> y <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> contiene una referencia al objeto de contenido que se navega.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Además, el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> propiedad será `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene y establece el objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> que está asociado a la entrada del historial de retroceso de navegación de la página a la que se navega.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> asociado a la entrada del historial de retroceso de navegación de la página desde la que se navega.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> event is raised when navigating from one piece of content to another.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> evento se desencadena al navegar de una parte del contenido a otro.

trans-unit.source: The content that is being navigated from is added to back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: El contenido que se navega desde se agrega al historial de navegación hacia atrás.

trans-unit.source: You can set <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A> with a custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to associate state information with content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Puede establecer <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A> con un personalizado <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objeto que se va a asociar la información de estado con contenido en el historial de navegación.

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Object" /> de datos opcionales que se pasó cuando comenzó la navegación.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Object" /> de datos opcionales que se pasó cuando comenzó la navegación.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> puede utilizarse para pasar datos específicos del contexto que son específicos para una navegación determinada.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A> contiene una referencia al objeto que se pasa como segundo argumento al llamar a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> o <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: De lo contrario, es `null`.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the navigator (<see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Frame" />) that is specified by <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator" /> is servicing this navigation, or whether a parent navigator is doing so.
trans-unit.target: Indica si el navegador (<see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow" />, el objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Frame" />) especificado por <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator" /> está atendiendo esta navegación o si lo está haciendo un navegador primario.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that is <see langword="true" /> if the navigator that is specified by <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator" /> is servicing this navigation.
trans-unit.target: Valor <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que es <see langword="true" /> si el navegador especificado por <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator" /> está atendiendo esta navegación.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <see langword="false" /> is returned, such as during a nested <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Frame" /> navigation.
trans-unit.target: De lo contrario, se devuelve <see langword="false" />, como ocurre durante una navegación de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Frame" /> anidada.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode" /> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode" /> que indica el tipo de navegación que tiene lugar.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode" /> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: Valor <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode" /> que indica el tipo de navegación que tiene lugar.

trans-unit.source: The types of navigation that can occur are:
trans-unit.target: Los tipos de navegación que se pueden producir son:

trans-unit.source: Navigating to new content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.New>).
trans-unit.target: Navegar al nuevo contenido (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.New>).

trans-unit.source: Navigating to the previous item in back navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Back>).
trans-unit.target: Navegar al elemento anterior en la parte posterior de historial de navegación (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Back>).

trans-unit.source: Navigating to the next item in forward navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Forward>).
trans-unit.target: Desplácese hasta el elemento siguiente en el historial de navegación hacia atrás (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Forward>).

trans-unit.source: Refreshing existing content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Refresh>).
trans-unit.target: Actualizar el contenido existente (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode.Refresh>).

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: Navegador que generó este evento.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Object" /> que es el navegador que generó este evento.

trans-unit.source: While <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> stores a reference to the navigator that raised this event, the navigator may not have actually initiated the navigation.
trans-unit.target: Mientras <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> almacena una referencia al navegador que generó este evento, el explorador puede realmente no haya iniciado el panel de navegación.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether this navigator did initiate the current navigation, inspect the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Para determinar si este navegador inició la navegación actual, inspeccione el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> que se va a aplicar al contenido al que se navega.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState" /> que se va a aplicar al contenido al que se navega.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A> will contain a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object if navigating to content in back or forward navigation history that has a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object associated with it.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A> contendrá un <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> si se navega al contenido en la parte posterior de un objeto o reenviar el historial de navegación que tiene un <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objeto asociado a él.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] del contenido al que se navega.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> del contenido al que se navega.

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Si se navega a un objeto, <see cref="P:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri" /> es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Puede navegar al contenido mediante una [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] o un objeto.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> contains the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Cuando se desplace a una [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], que se produce cuando se llama a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> y <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> contiene el [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] del contenido que se navega.

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Además, el <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> propiedad será `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.WebRequest" /> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.WebRequest" /> que se usa para solicitar el contenido especificado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.WebRequest" /> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.WebRequest" /> que se usa para solicitar el contenido especificado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=nameWithType> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a Web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=nameWithType> es una clase base abstracta que encapsula una solicitud Web y es independiente del protocolo.

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the .NET Framework includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=nameWithType> and extends it with protocol specific state and behavior, including:
trans-unit.target: Para cada protocolo, .NET Framework incluye una clase que deriva de <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=nameWithType> y se extiende con comportamiento y estado específicos de protocolo, incluidos:

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md)).
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizan el `pack://` esquema para solicitar archivos de datos de aplicación (consulte [recursos de la aplicación de WPF, contenido y archivos de datos](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md)).

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizan el `http://` esquema para solicitar archivos de servidores Web.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizan el `ftp://` esquema para solicitar archivos de servidores FTP.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizan el `file://` esquema para solicitar archivos locales.

trans-unit.source: You can both view and modify <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> details.
trans-unit.target: Puede ver y modificar <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> detalles.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.WebRequest%2A> is `null` when navigation occurs by:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.WebRequest%2A> es `null` cuando se produce la navegación por:

trans-unit.source: Using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control.
trans-unit.target: Mediante el <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control.

trans-unit.source: Calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>
trans-unit.target: Una llamada a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Setting <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Establecer <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Navigating through HTML content in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: Desplazarse por el contenido HTML en una <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
